is there a redirect on the image url?

I typically export all data in hubdb to a csv, delete all data, then reupload

I also will just export data, create a new table, import the data to new table, then change the target for the data and see if that changes anything.

If not, then I’d guess something in the code or something really odd

Your custom object likely has some required fields for creation. If you have those required fields, and you have an association made, it should create a new custom object record and attach it to your contact
